#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dialogs"
msgstr "Dijalozi"

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Palette Manager Dialog"
msgstr "Upravitelj paletama"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The palette manager allows you to add, remove or swap flosses from your "
"current palette and the selected scheme. You can remove all non used flosses "
"from your current palette and you are able to add new flosses to the scheme. "
"Additionally you can bring up <link linkend=\"CalibrateDialog\">the floss "
"calibration dialog</link> from here."
msgstr ""
"Upravitelj paleta vam omogućava da dodate, uklonite ili zamijenite konce od "
"vaše trenutne palete i odabrane sheme. Možete ukloniti sve konce koje nisu "
"iskorišteni  od vaše trenutne palete, a vi ste u mogućnosti da dodate  nove "
"koce šemi. Osim toga možete dovesti do <link linkend=\"CalibrateDialog\"> "
"konac za kalibrirani dijalog </link> odavde."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can allocate the number of strands of cotton used for each floss, for "
"both stitching and backstitching. This information will be used in "
"calculating the amount of floss required in the final design."
msgstr ""
"Možete dodijeliti broj niti od pamuka korištene za svaki konac, za svako "
"šivanje i za duplo šivanje. Ove informacije će se koristiti u obračunavanju "
"količine  konca potrebne na kraju dizajniranja."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog includes a <guilabel>Pick Color</guilabel> button which allows "
"selection of a color from anywhere on screen. This could be from a "
"background image for example to allow easy selection of matching colors. The "
"cursor will change to a cross with a color swatch indicating the color of "
"the pixel under the cross. After clicking on a pixel, a floss that closely "
"matches the selected color will be selected in the flosses list."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbol Selector"
msgstr "Simbol Selektor"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each of the flosses you can allocate a symbol. The symbol selector "
"dialog shows all the available symbols. Used symbols are shown grayed out "
"and a tooltip will show <quote>Used</quote> when the symbol is hovered over. "
"For the palette, the symbol library used can also be changed by selecting "
"one from the drop down list. All the flosses will then be allocated a symbol "
"from the new library."
msgstr ""
"Za svaki konac možete dodijeliti simbol. Dijalog simbol selektor prikazuje "
"sve dostupne simbole. Korišteni simboli su prikazani sivom bojom i  na "
"oblačiću će se pokazati <quote> Korišteni</quote> kada se simbol nalazi "
"iznad. Za palete, simbol knjižnica također se može promijeniti, izborom "
"jedne iz padajuće liste. Svi konci će biti izdvojeni simbol iz nove "
"biblioteke."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "The New Color Dialog"
msgstr "Boja novog dijaloga"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog shows the name of the scheme that the new color will be added to. "
"The color requires a name and a description, which can be anything you want, "
"although color name will usually be defined by the floss manufacturer."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog prikazuje ime sheme i da će nova boja biti dodana u tu shemu. Boja "
"zahtijeva ime i opis, koji može biti sve što želite, iako naziv boje obično "
"definiše proizvođač konca."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the <guilabel>Color</guilabel> button will show a standard "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/colors.html\">&kde; color selection dialog</"
"ulink>. The initial color can be selected and then the parameters can be "
"adjusted to give the correct color."
msgstr ""
"Klikom na <guilabel> Boja </guilabel> gumb će pokazati standard <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/colors.html\"> &kde; dijalog za izbor boja </ulink> , "
"Početne boje mogu biti izabrane, a zatim se parametri mogu prilagoditi na "
"odgovarajuće boje."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once added this new color will be available to be included in your patterns "
"palette via the <guilabel>Palette Manager</guilabel> dialog. It may also be "
"adjusted by using the <link linkend=\"CalibrateDialog\">Floss Calibration "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kada je dodana nova boja, ona će biti dostupna da se uključi u svom obrascu "
"paleta preko <guilabel> Upravitelj paletama </guilabel> dijalog. Također se "
"može podesiti pomoću <link linkend=\"CalibrateDialog\"> Kalobracija konca za "
"dialog </link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Floss Calibration Dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog kalibracije konca"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "This dialog has two parts."
msgstr "Dijalog koji ima dva dijela."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left, a pick list of the schemes that are currently available along "
"with a list of colors that are in that scheme. The color description will be "
"appended with <guilabel>(Calibrated)</guilabel> if the color has been "
"modified by the current invocation of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Na lijevoj strani, nalazi se lista za odabir šema koje su trenutno dostupne "
"uz popis boja koje su u toj šemi. Opis boja će se dodati sa <guilabel> "
"(kalibrirani) </guilabel> ako je boja izmijenjena trenutnim prizivanjem ovog "
"dijaloga."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right, is the name and description of the currently selected color, "
"this will be appended with <guilabel>(Modified)</guilabel> if the color has "
"been modified, a preview of the color, and the current RGB values for the "
"color."
msgstr ""
"Na desnoj strani je ime i opis trenutno odabrane boje, to će se dodati sa "
"<guilabel> (Promjena) </guilabel> ako je boja izmijenjena,  tu se nalazi "
"pregled boje i trenutni RGB vrijednosti za boje."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also shown is a <guibutton>Reset Color</guibutton> button. This will reset "
"the currently selected color to the value it had when the dialog was first "
"invoked."
msgstr ""
"Također je prikazano <guibutton> Resetiraj boju </guibutton>. Ovo će "
"resetirati trenutno izabranu boju na vrijednost koju je imala kada je prvi "
"put pozvan dijalog."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button will commit all of the changed "
"colors."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom na <guibutton> OK </guibutton> će izvršiti sve promjene boja."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> button will restore all the "
"changed colors back to their original values."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom na <guibutton> Odustani </guibutton> će vratiti sve promijenjene "
"boje natrag u njihove prvobitne vrijednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Configuration Dialog"
msgstr "Konfiguracijski dijalog"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "This dialog lets you configure a number of elements of KXStitch."
msgstr "Ovaj dijalog vam omogućava da konfigurirate broj elemenata KXStitch."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the options are self explanatory. The check boxes enable or disable "
"various functions or elements. The pick lists allow selection of the "
"required format of those elements."
msgstr ""
"Većina opcije su samoobjašnjavajuće. Polja za potvrdu omogućavaju ili "
"onemogućavaju različite funkcije ili elemente. Liste za odabir omogućavaju "
"izbor traženom formatu tih elemenata."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:101
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can return to the default set of parameters using the "
#| "<guibutton>Default</guibutton> button."
msgid ""
"You can return to the default set of parameters using the "
"<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Možete se vratiti na default skup parametara koristeći <guibutton> Default </"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Import Image Dialog"
msgstr "DIjalog za uvoz slike"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left of the dialog there is a preview of the imported image, based on "
"the parameters on the right."
msgstr ""
"Na lijevoj strani dijaloga postoji pregled ubačenih slika, na osnovu "
"parametara na desnoj strani."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The floss scheme for the finished pattern can be selected, by default this "
"is the same as the <guilabel>New Pattern Properties</guilabel> dialog "
"defaults. The maximum colors to be used for the pattern can be enabled and "
"changed as required, by default the imported pattern will have as many "
"colors as are defined in the original image that are converted to floss "
"colors. Checking the <guilabel>Ignore Color</guilabel> box allows you to "
"click the dropper tool to select a color in the image that will be ignored "
"on import. This is useful to remove backgrounds that you don't need "
"converting to stitches. The ignored color will be displayed as a checker "
"board pattern in the preview."
msgstr ""
"Mogu biti izabrane šema konac za gotov uzorak, po defaultu to je isto kao i "
"<guilabel> Svojstva novih obrazaca </guilabel> dijalog vrijednosti. Boje "
"koje će se koristiti za uzorak mogu biti uključene i promjenjene po potrebi, "
"po defaultu uvezeni obrazac će imati što više boja kao što su definirani u "
"originalnim slikama koje se pretvaraju u konac boje. Uključenje <guilabel> "
"Ignoriši boje </guilabel> kućice vam omogućava da kliknete na četkicu koja "
"je alat za odabir boje u sliku koja će se zanemariti pri uvozu. To je "
"korisno za uklanjanje pozadine bez pretvaranja u šavove. Zanemarena boja će "
"biti prikazana kao šahovska tabla obrazcu za pregled."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The cloth count value defaults to the <guilabel>New Pattern Properties</"
"guilabel> dialog and the scale is set such that the final size is as close "
"to the <guilabel>New Pattern Properties</guilabel> pattern size as possible. "
"These values can be changed as required."
msgstr ""
"Vrijednost broja tkanine ima se postavlja prema <guilabel> Svojstva novih "
"obrazaca </guilabel> dijalogu a skala se postavljena tako da je konačna "
"veličina približna veličini uzorka iz<guilabel> Svojstva novih obrazaca </"
"guilabel> što je bliže moguće. Ove vrijednosti mogu se mijenjati po potrebi."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Crop image</guilabel> checkbox enables cropping of the preview "
"image. Click and drag across the preview image to select the area required. "
"Guide lines are shown before selecting the starting point to allow more "
"accurate placement. Once an area is selected the preview will be rerendered "
"to show the cropped area. Further cropping can be done if required. Clicking "
"on the reset button, or turning off cropping will revert the preview to the "
"original image."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Use fractionals</guilabel> checkbox will enable the use of "
"fractional stitches in the imported pattern. This effectively doubles the "
"import resolution without affecting the overall size of the pattern."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> koristi razlomke </guilabel> će omogućiti korištenje frakcijskih "
"šavova i uvoze u obrascu. To zapravo udvostručuje rezoluciju uvoza bez "
"utjecaja na ukupnu veličinu uzorka."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:137
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking <guibutton>Import</guibutton> will convert the image into a "
#| "pattern."
msgid ""
"Clicking <guibutton>OK</guibutton> will convert the image into a pattern."
msgstr "Klikom na <guibutton>Uvezi</guibutton> će pretvoriti sliku u obrazac."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Properties Dialog"
msgstr "Izbornik svojstava za datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pattern size can be defined in units of stitches, centimeters or inches. "
"The width and height values will updated automatically to the equivalent "
"size in the new unit type if the units type is changed."
msgstr ""
"Veličina obrasca se može definirati u jedinicama šavova, centimetara ili "
"inča. Širina i visina će se automatski ažurirati na ekvivalentnu veličinu i "
"jedinicu koja predstavlja tu veličinu."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The cloth count is defined in units per centimeter or inches and is "
"dependent on the units of size. &ie; if CM is selected for the units then "
"cloth count will be in units per centimeter, similarly for inches. If the "
"<guilabel>Units</guilabel> is changed to <guimenuitem>Stitches</guimenuitem> "
"then the cloth count units will remain as the last CM or inches value."
msgstr ""
"Tkanina  je definirana u jedinicama po centimetru ili inčima i ovisi o "
"jedinicama veličine. &ie; ako je  CM odabrana za jedinicu, tada će tkanina "
"biti izražena u centimetrima, slično za inče. Ako je <guilabel> jedinice </"
"guilabel> mijenja se  u <guimenuitem> Stitches </guimenuitem> onda će "
"jdinice tkanine ostati kao posljednji CM ili inčna vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Title, Author, Copyright and Fabric fields are free text, so you can "
"enter anything you like here. The fabric color can be set by pressing the "
"color button and selecting the required color. This will then be shown in "
"the editor and preview windows."
msgstr ""
"Naziv, autor, autorska prava  i fabrička polja su slobodni tekst, tako da "
"možete otvoriti sve što vam se ovdje sviđa. Fabrička boja se  može  podesiti "
"pritiskom dugmeta za boju i odabirom željene boju. Ovo će biti prikazano u "
"Windows uredniku i pregledniku."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The floss scheme has a pick list for all the available floss schemes, "
"including any that you have defined yourself."
msgstr ""
"Končana shema ima listu dohvatanja za sve dostupne šeme konaca, uključujući "
"i onu koju ste sami definisali."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Instructions</guilabel> tab can be used to enter any specific "
"instructions for sewing the pattern."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>instrukcije</guilabel> tabovi mogu biti korišteni za unos bilo "
"koje specifične instrukcije za prišivanje obrazaca."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Pattern Library Dialog"
msgstr "Biblioteka obrazaca"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Pattern Library Manager has a hierarchical tree view (more of a forest "
"really) of categories on the left with an icon view of the selected category "
"of patterns on the right. This dialog is non modal and can be left open "
"whilst working on the pattern."
msgstr ""
"Upravitelj bibliotekom obrazaca ima pogled na hijerarhijsko stablo "
"kategorija na lijevoj strani sa ikonom za pregled odabrane  kategorije "
"obrazaca na desnoj strani. Ovaj dijalog je nemodalanl i može se ostaviti "
"otvoren za vrijeme rada na obrascu."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The simplest way to use the library patterns is to drag and drop them onto "
"the pattern space. Alternatively using the &RMB; on a library pattern will "
"show a context menu with an option to copy it, this can then be pasted into "
"the pattern as many times as required."
msgstr ""
"Najjednostavniji način za korištenje uzoraka biblioteke je povlačenje i "
"ispuštanje uz prostor za obrazac. Alternativna upotreba &RMB; na biblioteci "
"uzoraka ce se pojavit sadržajni meni sa opcijom za kopiranje, nakon toga "
"može biti zalijepljeno unutar uzorka onoliko puta koliko je potrebno."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional items on the context menu are:"
msgstr "Dodatne ikone na sadržajnom meniju su:"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete: Delete a library item, for which a confirmation dialog is shown."
msgstr ""
"Izbrisati: Izbrisati ikonu biblioteke, za koju je prikazan dijalog potvede."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties: Show the properties dialog for the item."
msgstr "Karakteristike: Pokazane na dijalogu karakteristike za ikonu."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The properties dialog for each item displays its size and the floss scheme "
"used, the baseline value and the associated keyboard character. The baseline "
"is used to position the character pattern vertically relative to the cursor "
"position when using the Alphabet tool. Positive values move it down, "
"negative values move it up. The associated character is only required for "
"use with the Alphabet tool. After clicking in the associated character text "
"box, the next key press, including modifiers (&Shift;, &Ctrl;, &etc;) is "
"used as the key."
msgstr ""
"Karakteristike za svaku stavku prikazuju svoje veličine i šeme koje konac "
"koristi, osnovne vrijednosti i pripadajuće znakove sa tastature. U osnovi se "
"koristi za pozicioniranje karaktera obrazac vertikalno u odnosu na poziciju "
"kursora kada koristite Abecedni alat. Potrebno je vrijednosti premjestiti "
"dolje, negativne vrijednosti pokrenuti ka gore. Pridruženi karakter je "
"potrebn samo za korištenje abecendnog alata. Nakon što kliknete u polje za "
"tekst u vezi karaktera, sljedeći taster, uključujući i modifikatore "
"(&Shift;, &Ctrl;, &etc;) se koriste kao ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create new libraries by clicking the &RMB; on either an existing category, "
"to create a sub category, or on a blank area of the library list, for a new "
"top level category, and select the <guimenuitem>New Category</guimenuitem> "
"option, enter the name and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Kreirajte nove biblioteke klikom na &RMB; na bilo postojeću kategoriju, da "
"se stvore podkategorije, ili na prazno područje liste biblioteke, za novi "
"nivo kategoriju vrhu, i odaberite <guimenuitem> Nova kategorija </"
"guimenuitem> opciju, unesite ime i kliknite <guibutton > OK </guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a new library pattern by selecting an area in the pattern editor, "
"select copy, then use the &RMB; on an existing category and select paste. If "
"necessary you can use the properties option to add an associated key if you "
"want to use it as a character library."
msgstr ""
"Stvara novu biblioteku obrazaca odabirom na oblast u editoru obrasca, "
"odaberite opciju Kopiraj, zatim koristite &RMB; na postojećoj kategoriji i "
"odaberite opciju Umetni. Ako je potrebno možete koristiti opciju svojstva i "
"dodati odgovarajući ključ ako želite da ga koristite kao biblioteku znakova."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Library patterns can be dragged and dropped to other libraries in the list "
"to allow you to rearrange them to your needs. Note that there is no checks "
"to ensure that the key codes assigned to library patterns is unique and you "
"should modify any that duplicate an existing one."
msgstr ""
"Obrasci biblioteka mogu se vući i otpustiti na drugim bibliotekama u listi "
"koji vam omogućuju da ih preuredite po Vašim potrebama. Imajte na umu da ne "
"postoji provjera kako bi se osiguralo da se ključ kod dodijeljen biblioteci "
"obrazaca bude jedinstven i ne treba mijenjati bilo koji dupliraju postojeće."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Text Dialog"
msgstr "Tekst dijalog"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:222
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The text dialog allows you to select a font and size, then enter the "
#| "text. Clicking <guibutton>OK</guibutton> closes the dialog and returns "
#| "you to the &kapp; window. Positioning the text is the same as pasting any "
#| "other element. Press the &LMB; on the canvas roughly where you want the "
#| "text, this will show a preview of the text, position the text exactly "
#| "where you want it, then release the &LMB;."
msgid ""
"The text dialog allows you to select a font and size, then enter the text. "
"Clicking <guibutton>OK</guibutton> closes the dialog and returns you to the "
"&kxstitch; window. Positioning the text is the same as pasting any other "
"element. Press the &LMB; on the canvas roughly where you want the text, this "
"will show a preview of the text, position the text exactly where you want "
"it, then release the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog tekst vam omogućava da odaberete font i veličinu, a zatim unesite "
"tekst. Klikom <guibutton>U redu</guibutton> zatvara dijalog i vraća vas na "
"&kapp; prozor. Postavljanje teksta je isto kao i ljepljenje bilo kojeg "
"drugog elementa. Pritisnite &LMB; na platnu otprilike gdje želite tekst, to "
"će pokazati pregled teksta, postavite tekst točno gdje želite, a zatim "
"otpustite &LMB;."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extend Pattern Dialog"
msgstr "Proširi dijalog obrazca"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to extend the pattern in various directions by a number of "
"cells. Enter the number of cells in the spin boxes and press <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> to extend the pattern."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se koristi za proširenje obrazca u raznim pravcima po broju ćelija. "
"Unesite broj ćelija u spin kutije i pritisnite <guibutton> OK </guibutton> "
"da produži obrazac."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Printer Dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog štampač"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog has a page list on the left showing a thumbnail for each of the "
"pages. The right panel contains the layout editor where the elements can be "
"placed. Each element is customizable using the context menu and can be "
"positioned and sized to suit your requirements."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog ima popis stranica na lijevoj strani pokazuje kraticu za svaku od "
"stranica. Desna ploča sadrži uređivač u kojoj se može postaviti element. "
"Svaki element je prilagodljiv koristeći kontekst meni i može biti postavljen "
"na veličine koje odgovaraju vašim zahtjevima."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a printer configuration template. Currently a similar one to KDE3 is "
"included."
msgstr "Odaberite konfiguraciju pisač. Trenutno sličan KDE3 koji je uključen."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Append a page - This will append a page at the end of the list."
msgstr "Dodavanje stranice - Ovo će dodati stranicu na kraju liste."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert a page - This will insert a page before the one currently selected in "
"the list."
msgstr ""
"Umetni stranicu- Ova naredba će umetniti stranicu prije stranice na kojoj se "
"trenutno nalazimo."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete a page - This will delete the page currently selected in the list."
msgstr ""
"Obrisati stranicu- Ovo će obrisati stranicu koja je trenutno označena na "
"listi."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select an element - Used to select elements for editing or resizing."
msgstr ""
"Označi element- koristi se za označavanje elemenata za editovanja i promjenu "
"veličine."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert a text element - Used to insert a text element onto the current page."
msgstr ""
"Ubaciti tekstualni element- Korisiti se za ubacivanje tekstualnog elementa "
"na trenutnu stranicu."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert a pattern element - Used to insert a pattern element onto the current "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Ubacite obrazac element - Koristi se za umetanje element obrazac na trenutne "
"stranice."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:256
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Insert a text element - Used to insert a text element onto the current "
#| "page."
msgid ""
"Insert an image element - Used to insert an image element onto the current "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Ubaciti tekstualni element- Korisiti se za ubacivanje tekstualnog elementa "
"na trenutnu stranicu."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:257
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Insert a text element - Used to insert a text element onto the current "
#| "page."
msgid ""
"Insert a key element - Used to insert a floss key element onto the current "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Ubaciti tekstualni element- Korisiti se za ubacivanje tekstualnog elementa "
"na trenutnu stranicu."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When adding elements, select the required element icon, then select the area "
"of the page that the element is to occupy by clicking and dragging with the "
"&LMB; from one corner to another. The properties of the element can be "
"viewed and changed using the context menu accessed by the &RMB;"
msgstr ""
"Prilikom dodavanja elemenata, odaberite potrebnu element ikonu, a zatim "
"odaberite područje na stranici koje želite da element zauzme klikom i "
"povlačenjem s &LMB; od jednog do drugog ugla. Svojstva elementa mogu se "
"vidjeti i promijeniti koristeći kontekst meni pristupa od strane &RMB;"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:264
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The elements can be resized by selecting them using the "
#| "<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"select-element-icon."
#| "png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, this will "
#| "provide a sizing rectangle around the element. The corners can be dragged "
#| "around to adjust the size or the whole element can be moved by clicking "
#| "and dragging using the &LMB;."
msgid ""
"The elements can be resized by selecting them using the select "
"tool<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"select-element-icon."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, this will provide "
"a sizing rectangle around the element. The corners can be dragged around to "
"adjust the size or the whole element can be moved by clicking and dragging "
"using the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Elementi se mogu mijenjati tako da ih odaberete pomoću <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref = \"select-element-icon.png \" format = "
"\"PNG \" /> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, ovo će pružiti "
"dimenzioniranje pravokutnika oko elementa. Uglovi mogu biti iskorišteni da "
"bi se podesila veličina ili cijeli element može biti premješten klikom i "
"povlačenjem pomoću &LMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:269
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The page has an associated properties dialog which allows setting the "
#| "page margin and the grid size and visibility."
msgid ""
"The page has an associated properties dialog which allows setting the page "
"margin and the grid size and visibility. The page margin provides a guide "
"for the placement of objects but does not prevent elements from being "
"positioned outside the defined margin."
msgstr ""
"Na stranici ima povezani dijalog svojstva koja omogućava podešavanje margine "
"stranice,veličine mreže i vidljivosti."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pattern Element"
msgstr "Izbornik obrazaca"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pattern element will show the arrangement of stitches on the grid. The "
"properties dialog can be used to configure how the stitches will be "
"displayed. This allows the element to display as a picture of the pattern or "
"as the working pattern showing the symbols."
msgstr ""
"Element obrasca će pokazati raspored šavova na mreži. Dijalog Svojstva može "
"se koristiti za konfiguriranje kako će biti prikazani šavovi. To omogućava "
"elementu da se prikaž kao slika uzorak ili kao radni uzorak za pokazivanje "
"simbola."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pattern element defaults to showing the whole pattern when it is "
"created. Using the properties dialog a selection of the required area can be "
"made in the preview window by clicking and dragging a selection area."
msgstr ""
"Element obrasca normalno pokazuje cijeli uzorak kada je stvoren. Koristeći "
"dijalog osobine, izbor potrebnog prostora se može izvršiti u prozoru za "
"pregled klikom i povlačenjem na izbor područja."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Map Element"
msgstr "Mapa"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The map element is used when the pattern spans multiple sheets. It shows the "
"area of the whole pattern that this element represents. It can be enabled in "
"the pattern element properties."
msgstr ""
"Element mape se koristi kada se uzorak proteže u više listova. To se "
"pokazuje na području cijelog obrazca koji ovaj element predstavlja. Može "
"biti omogućen u obrascu element svojstva."

#. Tag: title
#: dialogs.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Element"
msgstr "Tekstualni element"

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A text element can be used to add text notes to the pattern or to show "
"titles or comments. The text is configurable with fonts, color and "
"transparency. In addition a border can be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Tekstualni element se može koristiti za dodavanje teksta bilješke u obrazac "
"ili da se pokaže naslov ili komentar. Tekst je podesiv na fontove, boju i "
"transparentnost. Osim toga može biti prikazana ivica."

#. Tag: para
#: dialogs.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Text elements can also utilize variables which will be converted to "
"properties from the pattern."
msgstr ""
"Tekstualni elementi također se mogu koristiti kao varijable koje će se "
"pretvoriti u svojstva obrasca."

